Description: This package contains a Shiny app where users can explore
    whole-genome duplication (WGD) events in angiosperms, their dates,
    and phylogenetic positions. Users can visualize WGD events for clades
    of interest, download data, and explore posterior distributions for WGD
    ages for all WGD events in 466 angiosperm species.
